ght of sitting<br /></li><li>Bounce house</li><li>Games</li><li>Crafts</li><li>Face painting</li><li>Explore a police car, ambulance, fire truck and mobile SWAT command post<br /></li><li>And much more!</li></ul></ul><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">Make sure to vote for Rocket City Sitters in the Exhibitor Booth Competition!</span><span style="font-style: italic;">&nbsp; We look forward to seeing you there!</span><br /></div><br /><div style="text-align: center;"><font style="font-size: 8pt;"><a style="color: rgb(12, 71, 157); text-decoration: underline;" href="#Top" shape="rect">Back to Top</a></font><br /></div></font></td></tr></table><a name="LETTER.BLOCK11" /><table style="background-color: rgb(255, 209, 40);" bgcolor="#ffd128" border="0" width="100%" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0" id="content_LETTER.BLOCK11"><tr><td style="color:#333333;font-family:Trebuchet MS,Verdana,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:10pt;" styleclass="style_MainText" rowspan="1" align="left" colspan="1"><font color="#333333" size="2" face="Trebuchet MS,Verdana,Helvetica,sans-serif" style="color:#333333;font-family:Trebuchet MS,Verdana,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:10pt;">

